## WingLoop Repository

by leonardo avoni

After installation, you will have access to: Aswing Director and to WingLoop:
from WingLoop_Library import Aswing_Director
from WingLoop_Library import WingLoop
as well as the rest of the libraries and tools used within


## To install:
pip install -e .
(to be typed in the root folder of 02_WingLoop)
